Ilaretok oopishana


1  Ore apa te nena olong'i, eponari esiana oo looiteng'eni abul nejing olong'unyung'unyi erishata oo Lyahudi ooiro enkutuk oo Lgiriki o Lyahudi ooikini enkop enye. Ejo lelo loo Lgiriki eji eitololoikiaki inkolia enye te ndaa naorikini anaa ake. 
2  Neipot lelo Tomon o Aare esirit nalulung'a o looiteng'eni te nebo nejoki, “Meishiaakino te nikipal iyiook elikioroto o rorei le Nkai pee kitumoki aaisiaayia ltung'ana too mpesai. 
3  Ilalashera lang, entegelu intae iltung'ana oopishana liyiololo ti atua ate nchere kebore Enkiyang'et Sinyati nebore eng'eno, pee kincho lelo meitasheiki ena bae. 
4  Kake ore iyiook maate, enkomono kisheikino, o elikioroto e le rorei.”


5  Neitiship ina walata ilo turrur pooki; negelu Stefano, oltung'ani naa obore enkirukoto o Enkiyang'et Sinyati, Filipo, Prokorus, o Nikanor, o Timos, o Parmenas o Nikolaus, oltung'ani leme oloo Lyahudi laa Antiok eing'uaa, oibelekenye apa ninye ang'amu enkirukoto oo Lyahudi. 
6  Neriku ilo turrur lelo aarikoki Lkipaareta; ore pee eomon, neiteleikini nkaik. 
7  Neponari ororei le Nkai, ore esiana oo looiteng'eni neponari oleng te Yerusalem, ore ilapolosak kumok neunokino enkirukoto.

Eibung'aki Stefano


8  Ore Stefano, obore empiris o engolon, neas imbaa e nking'asia o olmonek ti atua olorere. 
9  Kake einyieito kulikae le nkaji e ntumo naji enoo Lkilakuno (amu neijia eji), o Lkirene, o le Aleksantria o Lkilikia o looing'uaa Asia, aaishankarrarre Stefano. 
10  Kake nelaikino aairisha eng'eno o Enkiyang'et nairorie Stefano. 
11  Nepuo too nkisudorot aarop iltung'ana ooetuo aajo, “Kitoning'o ninye eiro amor Musa, nemor Enkai.” 
12  Neinuaaki olorere, o lpayiani o laiteng'enak loo nkitanapat, nepuonu lelo enetii ninye, neibung aayaki enkiguana. 
13  Nesotu ltung'ana ooaku lchakenini le lejare, nejo lelo, “Megira ele tung'ani eitu esukeny ene wueji sinyati, nesukeny inkitanapat. 
14  Amu kitoning'o iyiook ninye ejo, eji keyooki ilo oji Yesu le Nasareti aar ene wueji, neibelekeny nkoon naaitanapa iyiook Musa.” 
15  Ore lelo pooki ootii ina kiguana pee eing'or enkomom e Stefano, neyia anaa enkomom o lmalaika.

